<para>Pure science computation for wesely scheme. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a pure computational kernel implementing Wesely 1989 gas dry deposition scheme. NO error checking, validation, or infrastructure concerns. Host model must ensure all inputs are valid before calling.</para>
